examples.en: The pressure varies with the depth.
The quality of health care varies greatly.
The cost of a room at the hotel varies with the season.
The general age of remounts varies from 3 - 5 years old.
The terrain varies as you climb higher.
The quality of the applicants varies widely.
Medical treatment varies greatly from state to state.
Mortality from heart disease varies widely across the world.
Your skin's moisture content varies according to weather conditions.
